		Space                  &amp; Comma &amp;                   //133 - Reference Transactions Flexfield Segment 3
		Space                  &amp; Comma &amp;                   //134 - Reference Transactions Flexfield Segment 4
		Space                  &amp; Comma &amp;                   //135 - Reference Transactions Flexfield Segment 5
		Space                  &amp; Comma &amp;                   //136 - Reference Transactions Flexfield Segment 6
		Space                  &amp; Comma &amp;                   //137 - Reference Transactions Flexfield Segment 7
		Space                  &amp; Comma &amp;                   //138 - Reference Transactions Flexfield Segment 8
