		Space                  &amp; Comma &amp;                   //145 - Reference Transactions Flexfield Segment 15
		Space                  &amp; Comma &amp;                   //146 - Link To Parent Line Context
		Space                  &amp; Comma &amp;                   //147 - Link To Parent Line Segment 1
