		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //071 - Interim Tax Segment 19
		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //072 - Interim Tax Segment 20
		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //073 - Interim Tax Segment 21
		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //074 - Interim Tax Segment 22
		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //075 - Interim Tax Segment 23
		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //076 - Interim Tax Segment 24
		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //077 - Interim Tax Segment 25
		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //078 - Interim Tax Segment 26
		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //079 - Interim Tax Segment 27
		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //080 - Interim Tax Segment 28
		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //081 - Interim Tax Segment 29
		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //082 - Interim Tax Segment 30
		Space                         &amp; Comma &amp;                           //083 - Interface Distributions Flexfield Context
